    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You counter a foe's blow by ripping out their sprouts, distracting them with pain. You can initiate this counter in response to an attack being made against you or an ally. If you are wielding a melee weapon, the foe or the ally must be within your reach. If you are wielding a ranged weapon, the foe or the ally must be within Close range of you. Make an attack roll against a DC equal to the foe's attack roll. If you succeed, the attack is negated and you may tear off 1 sprout from the attacker.</p>"
